      <title>PM说，缅甸要释放自11月以来举行的泰国渔民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/myanmar-to-release-thai-fishermen-held-since-november-pm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据泰国总理佩顿顿·辛瓦瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）称，缅甸政府已同意释放四名泰国渔民，他们于11月被海军拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/myanmar-to-release-thai-fishermen-held-since-november-pm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 02:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格斯在信号聊天云下开始高风险亚洲旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/hegseth-starts-high-stakes-asia-trip-under-cloud-of-signal-chat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）到达菲律宾，以五角大楼负责人的身份开始他的第一次来亚洲之旅，因为他面对民主党人辞职，以通过信号应用程序与其他美国官员分享攻击计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/hegseth-starts-high-stakes-asia-trip-under-cloud-of-signal-chat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 01:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nippon Steel Slumps在70亿美元的美国钢铁投资报告中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nippon-steel-slumps-on-report-of-7-billion-us-steel-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nippon Steel Corp.周五股价在一份报告中暴跌，该报告称，该公司正在考虑投资多达70亿美元，以升级美国钢铁公司，如果该设施赢得了其拟议的141亿美元收购的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nippon-steel-slumps-on-report-of-7-billion-us-steel-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:47:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示史密森尼网站擦洗种族，性别的内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-directs-smithsonian-sites-to-scrub-content-on-race-gender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项宣布，指示史密森尼机构（Smithsonian Institution）从其计划和展览中删除“不当意识形态”的参考，这是白宫最新努力，以打击有关种族和性别的教义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-directs-smithsonian-sites-to-scrub-content-on-race-gender</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普的压力下，密歇根大学碎片计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/university-of-michigan-scraps-dei-program-amid-trump-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根大学（University of Michigan）正在为特朗普政府施加压力放弃这种努力，并经过几个月的批评，并在其成本和有效性上批评了几个月后，就将其曾经宣布的多样性，公平和包容性计划取消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/university-of-michigan-scraps-dei-program-amid-trump-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普撤回美国资金的数十年艾滋病疫苗研究的水果损害了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/decades-of-aids-vaccine-research-imperiled-by-trump-s-withdrawal-of-us-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数十年的失败尝试，科学家对新一代艾滋病毒疫苗候选者最终将成功＆mdash感到乐观。自1981年以来，改变了大流行的过程，夺去了超过4200万的生命。但是，随着美国促进重要资金的努力，这种希望现在正在变暗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/decades-of-aids-vaccine-research-imperiled-by-trump-s-withdrawal-of-us-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:05:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普针对犯罪，在华盛顿特区非法移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-executive-order-creates-dc-task-force-on-crime-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周四签署了一项行政命令，为华盛顿特区（Washington DC）创建一个工作队，目的是解决犯罪和非法移民＆Mdash＆Mdash;一项针对他长期以来一直嘲笑暴力，失败和无序的城市的详尽行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-executive-order-creates-dc-task-force-on-crime-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 23:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在穆勒领带上针对律师事务所的律师事务所签署行政命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-signs-executive-order-against-wilmerhale-on-mueller-hire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四签署了针对威尔默哈尔（Wilmerhale）的行政命令，标志着总统针对与他的政治敌人或对其行为的调查有关的律师事务所的竞选活动的最新扩展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-signs-executive-order-against-wilmerhale-on-mueller-hire</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 22:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚的总理电话5月3日选举，民意调查显示紧密的比赛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/australia-pm-calls-election-for-may-3-as-polls-show-tight-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）于5月3日举行了一次选举，开始了一场紧密奋斗的运动，集中在生活成本压力和住房经济中的住房危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/australia-pm-calls-election-for-may-3-as-polls-show-tight-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 21:02:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对第三军事官员的报告“不知道”正在调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/china-unaware-of-reports-no-3-military-official-being-probed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国防部表示，有报道称该国第三军事官员被拘留是“不知道”的，因为他因腐败而受到调查的谣言被调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/china-unaware-of-reports-no-3-military-official-being-probed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 09:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
